{"lemma":"غَشْمِ","slug":"غَشْمِ","root":"غ.ش.م","root_slug":"غ-ش-م","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ش-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31889","n31890"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%92%D9%85%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31889","headword_ar":"غَشْمٌ","root":"g$m","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"treating, wrongfully, unjustly, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking"},{"kind":"text","text":"another's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property wrongfully,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by force:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking a course, in journeying"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at random, without direction and without knowledge."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) One says of a governor,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$ama Alr~aEiy~apa","text_ar":"غَشَمَ الرَّعِيَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", [accord. to the TK, the aor. of the verb in the sense here following is"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this I think a mistake,] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$omN","text_ar":"غَشْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beat, with vehemence, the people under his government, wrongfully, unjustly, injuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tyrannically, and took"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what he could."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$ama Aln~aAsa","text_ar":"غَشَمَ النَّاسَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He asked whom he could of the people."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$ama AlA^umuwra","text_ar":"غَشَمَ الاُمُورَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He performed affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a random manner,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confusedly, without discrimination."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 37: by implication.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$amahu","text_ar":"غَشَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smeared him"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. a camel]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with tar so that he left nothing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"no part of him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without tar, pouring it upon what was sound thereof and what was diseased thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$amN","text_ar":"غَشَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[perhaps as an inf. n., but accord. to the TK it is a simple subst., and the inf. n. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$omN","text_ar":"غَشْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of so smearing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ga$ama","text_ar":"غَشَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected firewood by night, cutting whatever he could get, without consideration,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) or, as in the A,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without discrimination."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n31890","headword_ar":"غَشَمٌ","root":"g$m","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the preceding paragraph.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Blackness"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of night: app. a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gasamN","text_ar":"غَسَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or, perhaps, a mistranscription]. (Ham p. 163.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}